%html
  %head
    %meta{ content: "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type" }
  %body
    %p
      = "Hi #{sanitize @student.first_name},"
    %p We hope that you are enjoying your trial.
    %p
      If you are finding our course useful but your personal circumstances makes it difficult for you to afford our course, you are welcome to apply for financial aid through our
      %b
        = link_to "Access Program", gamsat_preparation_courses_student_testimonials_url(anchor: 'student_improved_score')
      = "."
      The program is aimed at giving a helping hand to those in need and is open to a range of circumstance.
    %p
      Thousands of students each year choose GradReady. In addition,
      %b
        = link_to "8 years in a row,", gamsat_preparation_courses_student_testimonials_url(anchor: 'student_improved_score')
      the average GradReady
      %b
        = link_to "student improved", gamsat_preparation_courses_student_testimonials_url(anchor: 'student_improved_score')
      their score by
      %b
        = link_to "at least 20+ percentile points", gamsat_preparation_courses_student_testimonials_url(anchor: 'student_improved_score')
      after taking a GradReady course.
    %p
      We look forward to you being one of our many
      = link_to "success stories.", gamsat_preparation_courses_student_testimonials_url(anchor: 'student_improved_score')
  .trial_mail_footer
    %p Kind regards,
    %p GradReady Student Success Team
